rn Michigan University.</span></p>"], "第13回": ["<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border:none;\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"466\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:349.4pt;border-width:1pt;border-color:windowtext;padding:0cm 5.4pt;\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.15pt;text-indent:-26.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.18;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-pagination:none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\">【Core Weeks⑪】Face-to-face class《90minutes》</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.15pt;text-indent:-26.15pt;mso-char-indent-count:-2.18;mso-line-height-alt:0pt;mso-pagination:none;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">Business Disaster\n  Prevention<br /></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>", "<br /><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.15pt;font-size:11.0224px;text-indent:-26.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">Vulnerability of community businesses to environmental disasters</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.15pt;font-size:11.0224px;text-indent:-26.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">*Yang Zhang, Michael K. Lindell and Carla S. Prater</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:26.15pt;font-size:11.0224px;text-indent:-26.15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" times=\"times\" new=\"new\" roman\",serif;\"=\"roman',serif;'\" style=\"font-family:;\">Disasters, 2009, 33(1): 38−57.</span></p></div>"], "第14回": ["<div><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">【Core Weeks⑫】Face-to-face class《90minutes》</span></div>final presentation", ""], "第15回": ["<div><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">【Classes and examinatio